<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 12:20:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司的布鲁克斯跑步首席执行官将中国和欧洲视为增长领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/berkshires-brooks-running-ceo-sees-china-europe-growth-areas-2024-05-05/</link><description>布鲁克斯跑步公司的新任首席执行官表示，这家由沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司拥有的跑鞋制造商将中国和欧洲视为该公司在美国创收最多的业务的增长领域</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 10:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/berkshires-brooks-running-ceo-sees-china-europe-growth-areas-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>法国马克龙将就贸易和乌克兰问题向中国习近平施压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/frances-macron-set-press-visiting-xi-trade-ukraine-2024-05-05/</link><description>法国总统马克龙可能会敦促周日抵达巴黎进行罕见访问的中国国家主席习近平减少贸易失衡，并在乌克兰战争问题上利用他对俄罗斯的影响力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 00:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/frances-macron-set-press-visiting-xi-trade-ukraine-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔股东拒绝气候、多元化、中国提案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/berkshire-shareholders-reject-climate-diversity-china-proposals-2024-05-04/</link><description>周六，伯克希尔哈撒韦公司股东以压倒性多数否决了沃伦·巴菲特集团解决环境和社会政策问题的六项提案，这位亿万富翁投资者及其董事会都反对所有这些提案。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 21:52:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/berkshire-shareholders-reject-climate-diversity-china-proposals-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国化妆品行业期待习近平访华以缓和中国进口规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-cosmetics-sector-eyes-xi-visit-reprieve-chinese-import-rules-2024-05-04/</link><description>法国世界领先的化妆品行业指望习近平和马克龙下周举行会谈，以帮助最大限度地减少中国严格的新进口规则要求分享配方和制造技术对法国公司的影响。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 10:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-cosmetics-sector-eyes-xi-visit-reprieve-chinese-import-rules-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>前任命者表示，如果特朗普获胜，台湾将得到特朗普的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-have-trumps-support-if-he-wins-ex-appointee-says-2024-05-04/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普任命的一位前美国大使周六表示，他相信这位前总统如果重新入主白宫，将再次支持台湾。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 09:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-have-trumps-support-if-he-wins-ex-appointee-says-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>瑞信中国证券合资公司称2023年员工人数将减少46%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-china-securities-jv-says-staff-down-46-2023-2024-05-04/</link><description>瑞士信贷在中国的证券经纪合资企业表示，2023 年其员工人数将减少 46%，这一年瑞士当局安排了一次收购，以防止该公司倒闭。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 08:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-china-securities-jv-says-staff-down-46-2023-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>印度外交部长拒绝拜登的“仇外”言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-foreign-minister-rejects-bidens-xenophobia-comment-2024-05-04/</link><description>据《经济时报》周六报道，印度外交部长苏杰生驳斥了美国总统乔·拜登有关“仇外心理”阻碍印度经济增长的言论。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 05:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-foreign-minister-rejects-bidens-xenophobia-comment-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国 Zeekr 在美国 IPO 寻求高达 51.3 亿美元的估值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zeekr-plans-raise-up-368-mln-us-ipo-2024-05-03/</link><description>电动汽车制造商Zeekr智能科技控股公司周五表示，其在美国首次公开募股(IPO)的目标估值高达51.3亿美元，这是两年多来中国公司首次大规模上市。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 21:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zeekr-plans-raise-up-368-mln-us-ipo-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>小久保在伤停补时扑出点球，为日本队锁定冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kokubos-injury-time-penalty-save-secures-title-japan-2024-05-03/</link><description>日本队在周五以 1-0 击败乌兹别克斯坦队后，在伤停补时阶段由小久保扑出点球，为大岩刚的球队夺得了 23 岁以下亚洲杯冠军。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 20:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kokubos-injury-time-penalty-save-secures-title-japan-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人的幕僚长在美国承认欺诈罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/exiled-chinese-businessmans-chief-of-staff-pleads-guilty-us-fraud-2024-05-03/</link><description>流亡中国商人郭文贵的幕僚长周五承认与郭文贵合谋实施一项大规模计划，诈骗数千名投资者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/exiled-chinese-businessmans-chief-of-staff-pleads-guilty-us-fraud-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大调查发现外国干预选举的证据，但结果不受影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-probe-finds-evidence-foreign-meddling-elections-results-not-affected-2024-05-03/</link><description>根据周五公布的初步调查结果，官方调查发现加拿大最近两次联邦选举存在外国干预的证据，但投票结果并未受到影响，选举制度也很健全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-probe-finds-evidence-foreign-meddling-elections-results-not-affected-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称美国二次制裁旨在“遏制”中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-us-secondary-sanctions-aim-contain-china-2024-05-03/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部发言人玛丽亚·扎哈罗娃(Maria Zakharova)周五表示，美国正在利用对被视为与俄罗斯接触的中国企业实施二次制裁的威胁作为试图遏制北京的“借口”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-us-secondary-sanctions-aim-contain-china-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商赢得了在电动汽车税收抵免中使用中国石墨的延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</link><description>美国财政部周五为汽车制造商提供了对来自中国的一些重要微量矿物（例如石墨）的电动汽车税收抵免的电池矿物要求的额外灵活性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问之前，中国在法国电动汽车市场的份额下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</link><description>行业数据显示，法国政府减缓中国制造电动汽车涌入的努力正在取得成果，这突显了中国国家主席下周访问时最敏感的贸易问题之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟称三家中国电动汽车制造商提供的信息不足</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-information-three-chinese-ev-makers-insufficient-2024-05-03/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，欧盟委员会已警告三家中国电动汽车制造商，称他们没有为其反补贴调查提供足够的信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-information-three-chinese-ev-makers-insufficient-2024-05-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>